<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أَقْسَامُ الْمُعَارَضَةِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَالْمُعَارَضَةُ تَنْقَسِمُ إِلَى ثَلَاثَةِ أَقْسَامٍ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُعَارَضَةٌ فِي الْأَصْلِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمُعَارَضَةٌ فِي الْفَرْعِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمُعَارَضَةٌ فِي الْوَصْفِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">أَمَّا الْمُعَارَضَةُ فِي الْأَصْلِ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَبِأَنْ يَذْكُرَ عِلَّةً أُخْرَى فِي الْأَصْلِ سِوَى الْعِلَّةِ الَّتِي عَلَّلَ بِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>